ing: 1 (10 ounce) can diced tomatoes with green chile peppers
des: "This soup is not only pretty, it is very easy and healthy as well and truly delicious.  Top with chopped green onions and grated cheddar cheese."
ins: In a large saucepan over medium heat, cook onion, green and yellow bell peppers in oil until softened.  Stir in chicken broth, tomatoes, black beans, pinto beans and kidney beans.  Heat through.
